        Returns the Questionnaire page.
        Parameters:
        model - Spring Model object.
        user_id - cookie of the User.
        scenarioId - Integer indicating the identifier of a Scenario.
        lang - String, language code from locale cookie.
        language - String, language code passed as query-string parameter.
        Returns:

      • answerQuestion

        @RequestMapping(value="/answerQuestion",
                method=POST)
private java.lang.String answerQuestion(org.springframework.ui.Model model,
                                                                                                              @CookieValue(value="user_id",defaultValue="NULL")
                                                                                                              java.lang.String user_id,
                                                                                                              @ModelAttribute(value="question")
                                                                                                              int question_id,
                                                                                                              @ModelAttribute(value="answer")
                                                                                                              int answer_number,
                                                                                                              @ModelAttribute(value="comment")
                                                                                                              java.lang.String comment,
                                                                                                              @ModelAttribute(value="scenarioId")
                                                                                                              int scenarioId,
                                                                                                              @ModelAttribute(value="quiz_id")
                                                                                                              int quiz_id,
                                                                                                              @CookieValue(value="localeInfo",defaultValue="en")
                                                                                                              java.lang.String lang)
        Returns the fragment with the current Question to be answered. This function is called multiple times to load the different Questions regardless of where the user left off.
        Parameters:
        model - Spring Model object.
        user_id - cookie of the User.
        question_id - Integer indicating the identifier of a Question for which to record an Answer.
        answer_number - Integer indicating the identifier of the Answer given.
        comment - String, additional comment a User can leave under a question.
        scenarioId - Integer indicating the identifier of a Scenario.
        quiz_id - Integer indicating the identifier of a Quiz.
        lang - String, language code from locale cookie.
        Returns:
        "fragments/quiz-fragment :: question" string, specifying the Thymeleaf fragment to parse and return to the client.
